Class ImmutableDmaapConsumerConfiguration.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onap.dcaegen2.services.datafile.config.ImmutableDmaapConsumerConfiguration.Builder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DmaapConsumerConfiguration.Builder, DmaapCustomConfig.Builder<DmaapConsumerConfiguration,DmaapConsumerConfiguration.Builder>
    Enclosing class:
    ImmutableDmaapConsumerConfiguration

    public static final class ImmutableDmaapConsumerConfiguration.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
implements DmaapConsumerConfiguration.Builder
    Builds instances of type ImmutableDmaapConsumerConfiguration. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
